docs.lead_paragraph: A letter from Genoa, dated 29th Dec., mentions the arrival there of the American General SUMNER, charged, it was said, with a special mission to the King of Naples. HAYNAU is still at Florence, and much petted by the fashionabies.

headline.main: WALKS AMONG THE NEW-YORK POOR.; The Rag and Bone Pickers.

docs.lead_paragraph: This class, who number by the thousands, are nearly all Germans. Their head-quartersin are a part of the City almost utterly unknown to the great world--near the East River, in the Eleventh and Seventeenth Wards.
docs.snippet: This class, who number by the thousands, are nearly all Germans. Their head-quartersin are a part of the City almost utterly unknown to the great world--near the East River, in the Eleventh and Seventeenth Wards.

docs.lead_paragraph: Our streets are never cleaned. Our police force is inefficient, and our thoroughfares are obstructed by a thousand disagreeable obstacles. We walk in mire, sleep in fear, and run the risk daily of being trampled to death by infuriated oxen in our principal highways.

headline.main: MORAL AND RELIGIOUS.; Church and Miscellaneous Intelligence.

docs.lead_paragraph: Of the sum of $100,000, to be raised for the Union Theological Seminary, the Rev. Mr. GALLAGHER has succeeded in getting subscriptions to the amount of $75,000.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Ministers of Austria, Prussia and Russia have at length presented their credential letters to the Emperor. The Emperor of Russia remained firm in his refusal to use the term "Brother," and compromised by writing "Mon ami."
